Macros

#define FATFS_DRV_VERSION_ID   (0x0100000F)
 This is the mmcsd Driver Version. Versions numbers are encoded in the following format: 0xAABBCCDD -> Arch (AA); API Changes (BB); Major (CC); Minor (DD)
 
#define FATFS_DRV_VERSION_STR   "fatfs Driver Revision: 01.00.00.15"
 This is the version string which describes the FATFS driver along with the date and build information.
